name: THE FALL / DISILLUSION
description:
this is an old work I found while sorting my drive. hand-drawn on 2160x1080px display of a phone, this work was one of my early attempts on drawing digitally, and also one of my early works inspired by my interest in old buddhist paintings. with a little retouch, I decided to bring this work out and mint it for #HEN500k event.
